name: Amunets Dungeon Assets
description:
This mod adds new buildings for admin dungeons.
- generic dungeon encasement (ADA)
- various DungeonMaster (DM) inspired things.
- various Conan Assets (CA).

Big thanks to Germanny for the DungeonMaster stuff.

Discord @ https://discord.gg/a8hGAKW
changeNote:
2020-02-?? - 0.9.31
Fixes:
- "DM Lock (Gem Slot)" now correctly shows the gem and config.
- cut some corners on the stairs.
- fixed a rare bug with long trigger chains.

Added:
- "DM Lock (Item Slot)" which can trigger from items.
- "ADA Trigger Counter" which can be trigged by a certain amount. (use +1 / -1 as value to trigger)
